{"tid":2260480,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[馬丁開荒記]牛湖墩臨老入草叢","createTime":"2020-10-27T14:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T12:51:59.000Z","uid":64601,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7fdf10f71d3ec5b5f09eaca3d5075137ffa2f84b","tid":2260480,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"千！萬！不！要！行！牛！湖！墩！上個月做完山系男孩，今個星期日係時候做火系男孩。今次俾個frd揀，佢話行牛湖墩，上網睇都唔太難，點知真正行就真係出事啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期日坑口勁多人等車入西貢，的士都等咗個半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁塞車成粒鐘，仲要撞正撞車搞到中途要落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3SCbHwc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SCbHwc.png&h=435a82ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本諗住行紅線，點知黃線就被逼落車改行程<br />\n<br />\n[下面劇透]唔講咁多即刻開始！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4MPuoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4MPuoB.jpg&h=81d64f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錯有錯著，其實呢邊嘅景都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VtCZRCi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVtCZRCi.jpg&h=b88c1066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠哂疊馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6R042J4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6R042J4.jpg&h=c5dbb161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天空上行catwalk<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DGyBTQX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDGyBTQX.jpg&h=a987dbfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾我龜波氣功打到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFQHPpz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFQHPpz.jpg&h=ffda3de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟有冇人知係咩果實嚟，係咪有得壯陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBvwHKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBvwHKS.jpg&h=5867d2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到大枕蓋，個view好正同好大風<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8t6G4YZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8t6G4YZ.jpg&h=c8145da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落山到同屎忽瀡落去，唔記得影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後幾條友去挑戰牛湖墩，點知條路嘅入口係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bAEA9rL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbAEA9rL.jpg&h=d39124be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心諗仆街啦，條路仲要勁長，啲草仲長過我啲鳩毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZYRHNf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZYRHNf.jpg&h=528abed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲草仲要勁利，要用衫先開到路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Ja8K0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Ja8K0P.jpg&h=ebffbddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行咗半粒鐘，向上影落嚟連路都睇唔到咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到最後喺條路上俾棵擋住，被逼收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行返正路散下心咪算囉，行乜鬼牛湖墩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hzbWTUX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhzbWTUX.jpg&h=f184cf2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wATuuti.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwATuuti.jpg&h=78841d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drTY7eZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrTY7eZ.jpg&h=7ed44d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行完都五點，好彩當初冇繼續行入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d6cda91cf3319f840bcd2773d59795cdfd0183","tid":2260480,"uid":54647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"2520a5fcd9fb2813960ce531be2d9c23508afb65","tid":2260480,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"ok/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dd3ea70ed2f571d6b0876c3ed073b74c0e25a6","tid":2260480,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"0/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69841107cfc2e2c3ad6addc43f3977602dc44c6","tid":2260480,"uid":269910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"好笑/10"},{"pid":"67f83d35ad6d81d793f0bf8aa32a8e592d1f743b","tid":2260480,"uid":198652,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"你而家啲1Q題咁低質 憑咩自稱馬丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"